---
// CTA Section: Mid-page conversion point
---
<section class="py-12 md:py-16 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c0c0c] to-[#1a1a1a] border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] md:rounded-[3.5rem] p-8 md:p-16 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_30px_100px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)]">
            
            <!-- Decorative Background Glows -->
            <div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-600/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                    ¿Listo para transformar tu <span class="text-blue-500">infraestructura?</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-base md:text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium">
                    Agende una consultoría gratuita con nuestros expertos y descubra el potencial oculto de su tecnología.
                </p>

                <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
                    <form class="w-full group">
                        <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center bg-transparent md:bg-black/40 md:border md:border-white/10 rounded-2xl md:p-1.5 md:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 md:group-hover:border-white/20 gap-4 md:gap-0">
                            <!-- Input container: Styled on mobile -->
                            <div class="relative flex-grow w-full md:w-auto flex items-center pl-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0c0c0c] to-[#1a1a1a] border border-white/10 rounded-xl md:rounded-none md:bg-none md:border-none shadow-2xl md:shadow-none">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-blue-400/70 mr-3 transition-colors group-focus-within:text-blue-400">mail</span>
                                <input
                                    type="email"
                                    name="email"
                                    placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
                                    class="w-full bg-transparent border-none text-white placeholder:text-slate-600 focus:ring-0 py-4 md:py-3 text-sm md:text-base outline-none font-medium"
                                    required
                                />
                            </div>

                            <button
                                type="submit"
                                class="w-full md:w-auto bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-bold py-4 md:py-3 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/10 active:scale-95 border border-white/10 md:border-none"
                            >
                                Solicitar Información
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">
                        Garantía de respuesta en menos de 24 horas
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
